                     <interp inst="t17861213-102-person884" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I belong to Hyde-street office; I was present when the prisoner was examined at the Justice's; Mr. Oxley promised to forgive the <rs id="t17861213-102-deflabel510" type="occupation">boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861213-102-defend875 t17861213-102-deflabel510"></join> if he would make a confession; and he gave him a coat at the time.</p>
